Cyberpunk style: A vast holographic interface floating in a dark neon-lit space, displaying intricate cascading XML code structures transforming and morphing into new geometric patterns. Multiple translucent data panels arranged in a spiral formation, showing hierarchical tree structures on one side dissolving into reformed crystalline grid layouts on the other. Electric blue and magenta light traces flow between the panels like data streams, illuminating the transformation process. The scene is reflected on a glossy black surface below, with subtle circuit board patterns embedded in the floor. Floating geometric shapes representing data nodes pulse with cyan energy as they reorganize themselves automatically. The atmosphere is thick with digital particles and scanning lines, creating depth and movement throughout the composition.
